Reality star, Esther Agunbiade showed good spirits as she rocked her colleague and best friend in the BBNaija house, Frodd on the dance floor. Recall that some days ago, Frodd celebrated his birthday and Esther, his former love interest on the show wrote an emotional birthday message to him. This might be a positive sign between both parties as Frodd has always been open to dating the curvy young lady. In the video below, the reality stars were all loved up on the dance floor at an event. Source